### NduthiRide — Admin endpoints
### All routes require ADMIN role — get your token by logging in with an admin account.
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@adminToken = <paste_admin_access_token_here>
@accountId = <paste_account_id_here>
@riderId = <paste_rider_account_id_here>
@rideId = <paste_ride_id_here>
@parcelId = <paste_parcel_id_here>
@paymentId = <paste_payment_id_here>

### ─── Dashboard statistics ────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ─── List all accounts (paginated + filterable) ─────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/accounts?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Filter by role
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/accounts?role=RIDER&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Filter by active status
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/accounts?isActive=false&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Search by name or phone
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/accounts?search=kamau&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ─── Suspend an account ──────────────────────────────────────
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/accounts/{{accountId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isActive": false
}

### ─── Reactivate a suspended account ─────────────────────────
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/accounts/{{accountId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isActive": true
}

### ─── Verify a rider (approve documents) ─────────────────────
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/riders/{{riderId}}/verification
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isVerified": true
}

### ─── Reject a rider's verification ──────────────────────────
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/riders/{{riderId}}/verification
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isVerified": false
}

### ─── List all rides (paginated + filterable) ────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/rides?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Filter by status
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/rides?status=COMPLETED&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ─── Get a specific ride ────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/rides/{{rideId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ─── List all parcels (paginated + filterable) ───────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/parcels?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Filter by status
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/parcels?status=IN_TRANSIT&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ─── Get a specific parcel ───────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/parcels/{{parcelId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ─── List all payments (paginated + filterable) ─────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/payments?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Filter by status
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/payments?status=COMPLETED&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Filter by method
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/payments?method=MPESA&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
